title: Statement from the Press Secretary on the Visit of President Jean-Claude Juncker of the European Commission – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
July 17, 2018
President Donald J. Trump will welcome President Jean-Claude Juncker of the European Commission to the White House on July 25, 2018. The two leaders will discuss a wide range of priorities, including foreign and security policy, counterterrorism, energy security, and economic growth. President Trump and President Juncker will focus on improving transatlantic trade and forging a stronger economic partnership.
